e":"2018-03-12T00:20:19.000Z","msg":"呢個 project 收咗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3badfbe57031c29257e307b0211ea26dea337475","tid":589374,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5d736d56e7b2025962a9e263bb9171a79c308a0d","tid":589374,"uid":44358,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:20:19.000Z","msg":"呢個 project 收咗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"邊句講錯先?泛民打手?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1784f44682ee36dd86cf9386b3e9e41a1f653c","tid":589374,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:35:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5cbb0aa8a2aae75140e6fc86a811caeb810cd74","tid":589374,"uid":92230,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"小學雞你打我一下我打返你一下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲喺度分黨分派都on99"},{"pid":"c734bfc076ae7c1919fd1c9fcc12564b47b4a69a","tid":589374,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5cbb0aa8a2aae75140e6fc86a811caeb810cd74","tid":589374,"uid":92230,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"小學雞你打我一下我打返你一下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲喺度分黨分派都on99"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"選舉唔分黨分派選嚟做乜？<br />\n弱智唔好上連登做打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c666a3614f1cbf77db88e381079604d5bb64a3c","tid":589374,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e1e59ad9ed249642e943d626de529d6f23fe72","tid":589374,"uid":45285,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong> 祝賀關帝成功令被DQ既姚松炎入唔返立法會，幫保蝗手證明中共DQ有理！</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1868be0006884c06dd44abfdcabfb57d68ef314","tid":589374,"uid":57705,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03